{"tid":1534042,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【罷課罷工】聖瑪利學生冒雨派黑口罩、染紅紙巾　被禁足校門範圍","createTime":"2019-09-03T01:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T03:53:08.000Z","uid":307145,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd31145343bfd1134a9dab91735740e8f2d97f2","tid":1534042,"uid":307145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3230895/org/9014cc5711177117768ff1abfa7756f1.jpg/OSE9W8m4RuvY1u_cWP-VKGIBl217-Tc3VPZkRlT2ZEY?v=w1600r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3230895%2Forg%2F9014cc5711177117768ff1abfa7756f1.jpg%2FOSE9W8m4RuvY1u_cWP-VKGIBl217-Tc3VPZkRlT2ZEY%3Fv%3Dw1600r16_9&h=49703c85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日（2日）是新學年開學日，早上的狂風暴雨，未能洗去莘莘學子暑假期間反修例風波留下的烙印。律政司司長鄭若驊的母校嘉諾撒聖瑪利書院，亦有學生組成反修例關注組，今早在校門外派發黑色口罩及染紅紙巾，呼應今日的罷課行動；惟學生向《香港01》記者表示，校方沒收她們部分物資，亦不能在校內甚至校門附近派發。<br />\n<br />\n嘉諾撤聖瑪利書院則指，已酌情處理罷課，不會對學生作出處分。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3230682/org/408a66d93f833b28ba3eb99ca546588c.jpg/59LKtsh1G9p6f8pvngaLqMuGZ0aSRocoyxHihuER4oY?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3230682%2Forg%2F408a66d93f833b28ba3eb99ca546588c.jpg%2F59LKtsh1G9p6f8pvngaLqMuGZ0aSRocoyxHihuER4oY%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=b5c93913&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嘉諾撒聖瑪利書院反修例關注組，今早在校門外派發黑色口罩及染紅紙巾，呼應今日的罷課行動。期間，有學生戴上眼罩、黑色口罩及具備急救員字樣的白色頭盔。（梁鵬威攝）<br />\n<br />\n今日（2日）是新學年開學日，惟修例風波引起爭議至今仍未平息，中學生以及大專學界於今日發起罷課，以反映訴求。<br />\n<br />\n其中，律政司司長鄭若驊的母校嘉諾撒聖瑪利書院，亦有學生組成反修例關注組，今早在校門外派發黑色口罩及染紅紙巾，呼應今日的罷課行動。<br />\n<br />\n然而，有學生向《香港01》記者表示，校方沒收她們部分物資，亦不能在校內甚至校門附近派發。有老師曾向參與行動學生表示，不要妨礙其他同學的自由。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3230712/org/c10b20c41aed1b6565e15b0ff7634466.jpg/FDYXxcBqVU7Z-x2lWRIYV4l_LM1r5vv8waN4QeujeEE?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3230712%2Forg%2Fc10b20c41aed1b6565e15b0ff7634466.jpg%2FFDYXxcBqVU7Z-x2lWRIYV4l_LM1r5vv8waN4QeujeEE%3Fv%3Dw800&h=69a7e4e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3230714/org/ba62299dc9df735a269d987a6b1f00fc.jpg/mUj-zw_bzaIaO6x1nvMg7t1JHdQVe7LaX945k3XeOZM?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3230714%2Forg%2Fba62299dc9df735a269d987a6b1f00fc.jpg%2FmUj-zw_bzaIaO6x1nvMg7t1JHdQVe7LaX945k3XeOZM%3Fv%3Dw800&h=789b766d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3230713/org/24ca2cd4f229d4b75b04b201c41e4cb0.jpg/vLDVPLA9blv_Uh5OhyGtSlglaCgBQaRyGM8FuDLPBbg?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3230713%2Forg%2F24ca2cd4f229d4b75b04b201c41e4cb0.jpg%2FvLDVPLA9blv_Uh5OhyGtSlglaCgBQaRyGM8FuDLPBbg%3Fv%3Dw800&h=e3f58f36&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3230722/org/6a13a6ced26b3ff343c73c32cdb8b466.jpg/bvg0DWqXpYCE-DVTU6uhiJRMjZ_0dAn1XtDUYHTQ1GA?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3230722%2Forg%2F6a13a6ced26b3ff343c73c32cdb8b466.jpg%2Fbvg0DWqXpYCE-DVTU6uhiJRMjZ_0dAn1XtDUYHTQ1GA%3Fv%3Dw800&h=c6bd3747&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3230715/org/6152d02e18624f4d7989465dbe358fd3.jpg/LwHqOqx6rfQ_mjL6u4yUCc1cZ0sxNWojL8jb3QXI290?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3230715%2Forg%2F6152d02e18624f4d7989465dbe358fd3.jpg%2FLwHqOqx6rfQ_mjL6u4yUCc1cZ0sxNWojL8jb3QXI290%3Fv%3Dw800&h=05ca0105&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3230721/org/08129d9f18937400d53b99bd49ce54ca.jpg/INGuydVjKw89ecpgbfA_BpDDyb41wSr0F6zM-j2szPo?v=w800\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3230721%2Forg%2F08129d9f18937400d53b99bd49ce54ca.jpg%2FINGuydVjKw89ecpgbfA_BpDDyb41wSr0F6zM-j2szPo%3Fv%3Dw800&h=7f45b202&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n關注組在Instagram專頁的限時貼文中指，校方要求帶黑色口罩的學生換上普通口罩，有老師表明若不遵從則會被記大過。<br />\n嘉諾撤聖瑪利書院晚上發新聞稿，指校方原則上不鼓勵罷課，但了解罷課訴求，參與學生亦得到家長同意，故已酌情處理罷課，不會對學生作出處分。<br />\n<br />\n校方又指，為免令校內其他人產生不安情緒，故不認同學生在校內的大石級作連儂牆，以及佩載韓國立體口罩、蓋眼紗布、頭盔等物品。校方本著「寬容體諒」的精神，允許學生在雨天操場使用臨時流動壁報板，以張貼正面鼓勵字眼；並提供醫用口罩予學生更換，不會處罰曾佩載韓國立體口罩的學生。"},{"pid":"c276fdbda117cb8a1b0148f3dc3fcf8006e570c8","tid":1534042,"uid":1158,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:37:01.000Z","msg":"有老師表明若不遵從則會<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">被記大過</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家D 學生點會驚呢D ....進晒化啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571667103ed40476c2c018d20ac3bbf68bc4ab5f","tid":1534042,"uid":36378,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c276fdbda117cb8a1b0148f3dc3fcf8006e570c8","tid":1534042,"uid":1158,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:37:01.000Z","msg":"有老師表明若不遵從則會<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">被記大過</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家D 學生點會驚呢D ....進晒化啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:39:52.000Z","msg":"TG都唔驚會驚大過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68e61ed21f00beabe78148fb9752b28c2b9d47e5","tid":1534042,"uid":226913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"571667103ed40476c2c018d20ac3bbf68bc4ab5f","tid":1534042,"uid":36378,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c276fdbda117cb8a1b0148f3dc3fcf8006e570c8","tid":1534042,"uid":1158,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:37:01.000Z","msg":"有老師表明若不遵從則會<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">被記大過</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家D 學生點會驚呢D ....進晒化啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:39:52.000Z","msg":"TG都唔驚會驚大過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:12:45.000Z","msg":"坐監都未撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f15eb5ec2b96cb1fa291ed3ccfbbf98fd35d8d73","tid":1534042,"uid":258477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:53:08.000Z","msg":"【罷課風波】嘉諾撒聖瑪利書院校友公開信<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534379\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534379</a>"}]}